{"tid":1962417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港法官薪酬遠超英美，部份更超出3倍","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T04:25:38.000Z","uid":305299,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"3de294e2c9ad1c183b264d48eab891b78913478f","tid":1962417,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0XmFdu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0XmFdu.png&h=418d22d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以來，都有好多討論關於香港嘅法治情況，有部份人堅持話有險可守<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔理立場係點都好，依啲討論入面，好少會對比香港同外國法官嘅薪酬，但其實大家係應該要知道依啲數據先啱，所以查咗一查相關資料，整咗個表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔查都唔知，原來香港高等法院法官嘅月薪，比英國美國所有最高法院首席大法官都仲要高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且比較相同級別嘅美國州政府高等法院法官，高超出3倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到依啲數據之後，真係要為自己之前交嘅稅款流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係，如果人工咁鬼高，點解舊年香港政府仲要請一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有刑事紀錄</span></span>嘅人，來出任高等法院終身制法官 (&lt;==高浩文法官)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用同樣嘅錢，可以叫外國嘅首席大法官來做 (人地想唔想來香港當然係另一個問題)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但換一個角度來睇，香港其實已經腐敗到一個咩程度，先至會要出3倍嘅價錢，都只係搵到一個有案底嘅人願意來做法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====傳送門=====<br />\n高浩文法官之史蹟:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1725481/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1725481/page/1</a><br />\n美國2018法官薪酬 (各州平均數) (1/1/2018):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncsc.org/microsites/judicial-salaries-data-tool/home/Archives.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncsc.org%2Fmicrosites%2Fjudicial-salaries-data-tool%2Fhome%2FArchives.aspx&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=98c2f840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncsc.org/microsites/judicial-salaries-data-tool/home/Archives.aspx</a><br />\n美國法官薪酬 (聯邦):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscourts.gov/judges-judgeships/judicial-compensation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscourts.gov%2Fjudges-judgeships%2Fjudicial-compensation&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=720dbba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscourts.gov/judges-judgeships/judicial-compensation</a><br />\n英國2018薪酬:<br />\n<a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/831874/judicial-salaries-revised-14-nov-2018.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F831874%2Fjudicial-salaries-revised-14-nov-2018.pdf&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=83ec76ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/831874/judicial-salaries-revised-14-nov-2018.pdf</a><br />\n香港稅局2018/19匯率 (4月):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/tax/bus_aer19.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Feng%2Ftax%2Fbus_aer19.htm&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=293f3580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/tax/bus_aer19.htm</a><br />\n香港法官2018/19薪酬 (Appendix C):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jsscs.gov.hk/reports/en/jscs_19.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jsscs.gov.hk%2Freports%2Fen%2Fjscs_19.pdf&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=4c26d757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jsscs.gov.hk/reports/en/jscs_19.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jkLnrH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jkLnrH.png&h=210a4a5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi