，真係唔同context<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港legal sector真係蓬勃到而家其實都只不過係一百年都無，qualified 做judge嘅pool真係好細<br />\n我自己都對香港法治反感，但老實講如果法官人工低，真係對好多出色嘅資深大狀低吸引力，呢個真係好多大狀嘅concern，無呃你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你覺得佢地係狗官，我理解，我只不過係同你講啲法律界人士concern<br />\n你係咪想high court/appeal court/甚至乎終審法院都係班低能mag仔主持大局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"做乜喺呢啲post咁認真啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國個情況最離譜 <br />\n佢地出咗名法官人工嚴重偏低 <br />\n做到Supreme Court呢啲最頂層嘅法官 <br />\n人工都仲係連大firm嘅first-year associate都不如 新入行嘅勁人搵得仲多過最高級嘅法官"},{"pid":"104ddbf543f0fb66f899c1ebf7f61918169d133d","tid":1962417,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"月薪？屌你老母真係一堆垃圾"},{"pid":"5ad865455b7db18711bc6e588717aa733260404a","tid":1962417,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3bd4b69302114b7f771d0b2480ea91ebf71665","tid":1962417,"uid":189234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d47db21b12025253d964adb5cf2ef008bcb255a6","tid":1962417,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e004a9e013b05024728153da54ced4d5039511e","tid":1962417,"uid":189234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"Are you on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"律政司現正公開招聘<span style=\"color: red;\">法庭檢控主任</span>一職，此職位為公務員職位，主要是在裁判法院執行檢控工作，申請人<span style=\"color: red;\">無須持大學畢業</span>學歷，如成功受聘可獲起薪點$27,340的月薪。<br />\n<br />\n律政司法庭檢控主任的主要職責是在裁判法院執行檢控工作，並按上級指示執行一般法